<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>GDPR FAQs - D'amour Muslim | Data Protection & Privacy</title>
  <meta name="description" content="D'amour Muslim GDPR compliance and data protection FAQs. Learn how we protect your personal data, your rights under GDPR, and our privacy practices for Muslim matrimony services.">
  <meta name="keywords" content="GDPR matrimony, data protection Muslim marriage, privacy FAQ, personal data rights, UK data protection, matrimonial privacy">
  
  <!-- Open Graph / Social Media -->
  <meta property="og:title" content="GDPR FAQs - D'amour Muslim">
  <meta property="og:description" content="Learn about your data protection rights and how we keep your personal information safe on our Muslim matrimony platform.">
  <meta property="og:type" content="website">
  <meta property="og:url" content="https://damourmuslim.com/gdpr-faqs">

  <!-- Tailwind CSS -->
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/output.css">
  <!-- Remix Icons -->
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/remixicon@3.5.0/fonts/remixicon.css" rel="stylesheet">

  <!-- Custom CSS -->
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">

  <style>
    .faq-item {
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
    }
    .faq-item:hover {
      background-color: #f9fafb;
    }
    .faq-answer {
      max-height: 0;
      overflow: hidden;
      transition: max-height 0.3s ease-out, padding 0.3s ease;
    }
    .faq-item.active .faq-answer {
      max-height: 2000px;
      padding-top: 1rem;
    }
    .faq-item.active .faq-icon {
      transform: rotate(180deg);
    }
    .faq-icon {
      transition: transform 0.3s ease;
    }
    .gdpr-badge {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #3b82f6 0%, #1d4ed8 100%);
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body class="bg-gray-50 font-['Roboto']">
  <%- include('partials/header') %>

  <main class="pt-24 pb-16 min-h-screen">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6">
      <!-- Header Section -->
      <div class="text-center mb-8">
        <div class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-16 h-16 bg-blue-100 rounded-full mb-4">
          <i class="ri-shield-user-line text-3xl text-blue-600"></i>
        </div>
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4 font-['Playfair_Display']">GDPR & Data Protection FAQs</h1>
        <p class="text-gray-600 text-lg">Your Privacy Rights Explained</p>
        <p class="text-gray-500 mt-2 text-sm">Understanding how we protect and handle your personal data</p>
      </div>

      <!-- GDPR Compliance Badge -->
      <div class="gdpr-badge rounded-2xl p-6 text-white mb-8 shadow-lg">
        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-4">
          <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-white/20 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
            <i class="ri-eu-fill text-4xl"></i>
          </div>
          <div class="text-center md:text-left">
            <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">GDPR Compliant Platform</h2>
            <p class="text-white/90">
              D'amour Muslim is committed to protecting your privacy and complying with the General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR) and UK Data Protection Act 2018. Your data security is our priority.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Main Content -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl material-shadow overflow-hidden">
        
        <!-- GENERAL GDPR COMPLIANCE SECTION -->
        <div class="p-6 border-b border-gray-100 bg-blue-50">
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 font-['Playfair_Display'] flex items-center">
            <i class="ri-shield-check-fill text-blue-600 mr-2"></i>
            General GDPR Compliance & Security
          </h2>
        </div>

        <div class="divide-y divide-gray-100">
          <!-- FAQ 1 -->
          <div class="faq-item p-6" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
            <div class="flex items-start justify-between">
              <h3 class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-900 pr-4">Is my personal information secure on this platform?</h3>
              <i class="ri-arrow-down-s-line faq-icon text-gray-400 text-xl flex-shrink-0"></i>
            </div>
            <div class="faq-answer text-gray-600">
              <p class="mb-3">Yes, we take data security very seriously. Here's how we protect your information:</p>
              <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 ml-2">
                <li><strong>Encrypted connections:</strong> All data transmitted between your browser and our servers uses HTTPS/SSL encryption</li>
                <li><strong>Secure database:</strong> Your data is stored in secure database with access controls</li>
                <li><strong>Password protection:</strong> Passwords are hashed and encrypted—we never store plain-text passwords</li>
                <li><strong>Session security:</strong> Secure session management with HTTP-only cookies</li>
                <li><strong>Cloud security:</strong> Images are stored securely with automatic optimisation</li>
                <li><strong>Regular reviews:</strong> We regularly review our security practices and update them as needed</li>
              </ul>
              <p class="mt-4 text-sm text-gray-500">
                <i class="ri-information-line mr-1"></i>
                As a UK-registered company, we comply with UK Data Protection Act 2018 and GDPR requirements.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- FAQ 2 -->
          <div class="faq-item p-6" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
            <div class="flex items-start justify-between">
              <h3 class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-900 pr-4">Who can see my contact details?</h3>
              <i class="ri-arrow-down-s-line faq-icon text-gray-400 text-xl flex-shrink-0"></i>
            </div>
            <div class="faq-answer text-gray-600">
              <div class="bg-green-50 border border-green-200 rounded-lg p-4 mb-4">
                <div class="flex items-start">
                  <i class="ri-shield-check-fill text-green-600 text-xl mr-2 mt-0.5"></i>
                  <div>
                    <h4 class="font-semibold text-green-900">Your Privacy is Protected</h4>
                    <p class="text-green-800">Your personal contact details (phone number, email address) are <strong>hidden from all public users</strong> by default.</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <p class="mb-3">Here's who can access what:</p>
              <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 ml-2">
                <li><strong>Public users & other members:</strong> Cannot see your phone number or email address when viewing your profile</li>
                <li><strong>Accepted connections:</strong> Only users who you have mutually accepted can communicate with you through our secure chat system</li>
                <li><strong>Platform administrators:</strong> Our admin team can access your contact information solely to:
                  <ul class="list-disc list-inside ml-6 mt-1 space-y-1 text-sm">
                    <li>Verify your profile authenticity</li>
                    <li>Contact you regarding your account</li>
                    <li>Provide matchmaking services (for Premium members)</li>
                    <li>Handle support requests</li>
                  </ul>
                </li>
              </ul>
              <p class="mt-4 text-sm text-gray-500">
                Your private information is never shared with other users without your explicit consent.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- FAQ 3 -->
          <div class="faq-item p-6" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
            <div class="flex items-start justify-between">
              <h3 class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-900 pr-4">Do you verify user information?</h3>
              <i class="ri-arrow-down-s-line faq-icon text-gray-400 text-xl flex-shrink-0"></i>
            </div>
            <div class="faq-answer text-gray-600">
              <p class="mb-3">We do our best to verify user information and maintain profile quality:</p>
              <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 ml-2">
                <li><strong>Profile review:</strong> All profiles are reviewed by our team before being made visible to other users</li>
                <li><strong>Email verification:</strong> We verify email addresses through a code-based verification system</li>
                <li><strong>Photo review:</strong> Profile photos are reviewed for appropriateness and authenticity</li>
                <li><strong>Information checks:</strong> We review profile information for consistency and plausibility</li>
                <li><strong>Community reports:</strong> Users can report suspicious or fake profiles for investigation</li>
              </ul>
              <p class="mt-4 p-3 bg-amber-50 rounded-lg text-amber-800 text-sm">
                <i class="ri-information-line mr-1"></i>
                <strong>While we try our best</strong> to verify information, we cannot guarantee 100% accuracy of all user-provided data. We recommend families exercise their own due diligence when considering potential matches.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- DATA COLLECTION SECTION -->
        <div class="p-6 border-b border-t border-gray-100 bg-blue-50">
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 font-['Playfair_Display'] flex items-center">
            <i class="ri-database-2-fill text-blue-600 mr-2"></i>
            Data Collection & Usage
          </h2>
        </div>

        <div class="divide-y divide-gray-100">
          <!-- FAQ 4 -->
          <div class="faq-item p-6" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
            <div class="flex items-start justify-between">
              <h3 class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-900 pr-4">What kind of personal data do you collect?</h3>
              <i class="ri-arrow-down-s-line faq-icon text-gray-400 text-xl flex-shrink-0"></i>
            </div>
            <div class="faq-answer text-gray-600">
              <p class="mb-4">We collect the following categories of personal data to provide our matrimonial services:</p>
              
              <div class="space-y-4">
                <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-4">
                  <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2 flex items-center">
                    <i class="ri-user-line text-[#4a7c59] mr-2"></i>
                    Basic Account Information
                  </h4>
                  <ul class="text-sm space-y-1 ml-6">
                    <li>Username, email address, and password (encrypted)</li>
                    <li>Email verification status</li>
                  </ul>
                </div>

                <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-4">
                  <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2 flex items-center">
                    <i class="ri-profile-line text-[#4a7c59] mr-2"></i>
                    Profile Information
                  </h4>
                  <ul class="text-sm space-y-1 ml-6">
                    <li>Name, age, gender, date of birth, birthplace</li>
                    <li>Contact number and address</li>
                    <li>Physical attributes: height, build, eye colour, hair colour, complexion</li>
                    <li>Location: city, state, country, nationality</li>
                  </ul>
                </div>

                <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-4">
                  <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2 flex items-center">
                    <i class="ri-book-open-line text-[#4a7c59] mr-2"></i>
                    Religious & Cultural Information
                  </h4>
                  <ul class="text-sm space-y-1 ml-6">
                    <li>Religion, Islamic sect, caste, ethnicity</li>
                    <li>Religious practices (prayers, Milaad, Khatams)</li>
                    <li>Whether born Muslim or revert</li>
                    <li>Hijab/beard preferences</li>
                  </ul>
                </div>

                <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-4">
                  <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2 flex items-center">
                    <i class="ri-briefcase-line text-[#4a7c59] mr-2"></i>
                    Education & Career
                  </h4>
                  <ul class="text-sm space-y-1 ml-6">
                    <li>Highest education qualification</li>
                    <li>Work/profession details</li>
                    <li>Languages spoken</li>
                  </ul>
                </div>

                <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-4">
                  <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2 flex items-center">
                    <i class="ri-parent-line text-[#4a7c59] mr-2"></i>
                    Family Information
                  </h4>
                  <ul class="text-sm space-y-1 ml-6">
                    <li>Father's name and profession</li>
                    <li>Mother's name</li>
                    <li>Number of siblings and children (if any)</li>
                    <li>Marital status</li>
                  </ul>
                </div>

                <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-4">
                  <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2 flex items-center">
                    <i class="ri-heart-line text-[#4a7c59] mr-2"></i>
                    Preferences & Personality
                  </h4>
                  <ul class="text-sm space-y-1 ml-6">
                    <li>Partner preferences (age, height, ethnicity, etc.)</li>
                    <li>Lifestyle preferences and acceptance criteria</li>
                    <li>About me descriptions and hobbies</li>
                    <li>Future plans and living arrangements</li>
                  </ul>
                </div>

                <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-4">
                  <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2 flex items-center">
                    <i class="ri-image-line text-[#4a7c59] mr-2"></i>
                    Images
                  </h4>
                  <ul class="text-sm space-y-1 ml-6">
                    <li>Profile pictures and cover photos</li>
                    <li>Stored securely on Cloudinary with automatic optimisation</li>
                  </ul>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- FAQ 5 -->
          <div class="faq-item p-6" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
            <div class="flex items-start justify-between">
              <h3 class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-900 pr-4">How is my data used?</h3>
              <i class="ri-arrow-down-s-line faq-icon text-gray-400 text-xl flex-shrink-0"></i>
            </div>
            <div class="faq-answer text-gray-600">
              <p class="mb-3">Your personal data is used for the following purposes:</p>
              <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-3 ml-2">
                <li><strong>Profile display:</strong> To create and display your marriage profile to other registered users seeking matches</li>
                <li><strong>Matchmaking:</strong> To match you with potential compatible partners based on your preferences and criteria</li>
                <li><strong>Communication:</strong> To facilitate communication between matched users through our secure platform</li>
                <li><strong>Account management:</strong> To manage your account, verify your identity, and send important notifications</li>
                <li><strong>Service improvement:</strong> To analyse (in anonymised form) how our platform is used and improve our services</li>
                <li><strong>Customer support:</strong> To respond to your enquiries and provide assistance</li>
                <li><strong>Legal compliance:</strong> To comply with legal obligations and protect our rights</li>
              </ul>
              <p class="mt-4 p-3 bg-blue-50 rounded-lg text-blue-800 text-sm">
                <i class="ri-information-line mr-1"></i>
                We <strong>never</strong> sell your personal data to third parties for marketing purposes.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- FAQ 6 -->
          <div class="faq-item p-6" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
            <div class="flex items-start justify-between">
              <h3 class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-900 pr-4">Do you process "sensitive" personal data?</h3>
              <i class="ri-arrow-down-s-line faq-icon text-gray-400 text-xl flex-shrink-0"></i>
            </div>
            <div class="faq-answer text-gray-600">
              <p class="mb-3">Yes, some of the data we collect is classified as "special category" or "sensitive" data under GDPR:</p>
              <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 ml-2">
                <li><strong>Religious beliefs:</strong> Information about your religion, sect, and religious practices</li>
                <li><strong>Ethnic origin:</strong> Your ethnicity and nationality information</li>
                <li><strong>Health information:</strong> Any disability information you choose to provide</li>
              </ul>
              <p class="mt-4 mb-3"><strong>Legal basis for processing:</strong></p>
              <p class="text-sm">We process this sensitive data based on your <strong>explicit consent</strong>. By creating a profile and providing this information, you consent to us processing it for matrimonial matchmaking purposes. This data is essential for our service as it helps match you with compatible partners who share similar values and backgrounds.</p>
              <p class="mt-4 text-sm text-gray-500">
                You can withdraw your consent at any time by deleting your account.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- USER RIGHTS SECTION -->
        <div class="p-6 border-b border-t border-gray-100 bg-blue-50">
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 font-['Playfair_Display'] flex items-center">
            <i class="ri-user-star-fill text-blue-600 mr-2"></i>
            Your Rights Under GDPR
          </h2>
        </div>

        <div class="divide-y divide-gray-100">
          <!-- FAQ 7 -->
          <div class="faq-item p-6" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
            <div class="flex items-start justify-between">
              <h3 class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-900 pr-4">How can I remove my profile permanently?</h3>
              <i class="ri-arrow-down-s-line faq-icon text-gray-400 text-xl flex-shrink-0"></i>
            </div>
            <div class="faq-answer text-gray-600">
              <p class="mb-3">You have the <strong>right to erasure</strong> ("right to be forgotten") under GDPR. To permanently delete your account and all associated data:</p>
              <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-4 my-4">
                <div class="flex items-start">
                  <i class="ri-mail-send-line text-[#4a7c59] text-xl mr-3 mt-0.5"></i>
                  <div>
                    <p class="font-medium text-gray-900">Send an email to:</p>
                    <a href="mailto:contact@damourmuslim.com" class="text-[#4a7c59] hover:underline">contact@damourmuslim.com</a>
                    <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mt-2">Subject: <strong>"Account Deletion Request"</strong></p>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <p class="mb-3">What happens when you request deletion:</p>
              <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 ml-2 text-sm">
                <li>We will verify your identity through your registered email</li>
                <li>Your profile will be removed from public view immediately</li>
                <li>All your personal data will be permanently deleted within 30 days</li>
                <li>Any conversations and requests associated with your account will be removed</li>
                <li>Profile images will be deleted from our cloud storage</li>
              </ul>
              <p class="mt-4 p-3 bg-amber-50 rounded-lg text-amber-800 text-sm">
                <i class="ri-alert-line mr-1"></i>
                <strong>Note:</strong> Account deletion is irreversible. Please ensure you want to permanently remove your data before requesting deletion.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- FAQ 8 -->
          <div class="faq-item p-6" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
            <div class="flex items-start justify-between">
              <h3 class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-900 pr-4">Can I see all the data you hold about me?</h3>
              <i class="ri-arrow-down-s-line faq-icon text-gray-400 text-xl flex-shrink-0"></i>
            </div>
            <div class="faq-answer text-gray-600">
              <div class="bg-green-50 border border-green-200 rounded-lg p-4 mb-4">
                <div class="flex items-start">
                  <i class="ri-checkbox-circle-fill text-green-600 text-xl mr-2 mt-0.5"></i>
                  <div>
                    <h4 class="font-semibold text-green-900">Yes, absolutely!</h4>
                    <p class="text-green-800">Under GDPR, you have the <strong>right of access</strong> to your personal data.</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <p class="mb-3">How to request your data:</p>
              <ol class="list-decimal list-inside space-y-2 ml-2">
                <li>Send an email to <a href="mailto:contact@damourmuslim.com" class="text-[#4a7c59] hover:underline">contact@damourmuslim.com</a></li>
                <li>Use the subject line: <strong>"Data Access Request"</strong></li>
                <li>Include your registered email address for verification</li>
                <li>We will respond within 30 days with a complete copy of your data</li>
              </ol>
              <p class="mt-4 text-sm text-gray-500">
                You can also view most of your profile data directly by logging into your account and visiting the <a href="/account/info" class="text-[#4a7c59] hover:underline">account management page</a>.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- FAQ 9 -->
          <div class="faq-item p-6" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
            <div class="flex items-start justify-between">
              <h3 class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-900 pr-4">What if I want to update my information?</h3>
              <i class="ri-arrow-down-s-line faq-icon text-gray-400 text-xl flex-shrink-0"></i>
            </div>
            <div class="faq-answer text-gray-600">
              <p class="mb-3">Under GDPR, you have the <strong>right to rectification</strong>—the right to have inaccurate data corrected.</p>
              <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-4 my-4">
                <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">You can easily update your information yourself:</h4>
                <ol class="list-decimal list-inside space-y-2 text-sm">
                  <li>Log in to your account</li>
                  <li>Go to <strong>Account</strong> → <strong>Profile Info</strong></li>
                  <li>Or visit directly: <a href="/account/info" class="text-[#4a7c59] hover:underline">/account/info</a></li>
                  <li>Edit any fields you wish to change</li>
                  <li>Click "Save Changes"</li>
                </ol>
              </div>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">
                If you cannot update certain information yourself, or if you need help, please contact us at <a href="mailto:contact@damourmuslim.com" class="text-[#4a7c59] hover:underline">contact@damourmuslim.com</a>.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- FAQ 10 -->
          <div class="faq-item p-6" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
            <div class="flex items-start justify-between">
              <h3 class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-900 pr-4">What other rights do I have under GDPR?</h3>
              <i class="ri-arrow-down-s-line faq-icon text-gray-400 text-xl flex-shrink-0"></i>
            </div>
            <div class="faq-answer text-gray-600">
              <p class="mb-4">Under GDPR, you have the following rights:</p>
              <div class="space-y-3">
                <div class="flex items-start">
                  <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-blue-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mr-3">
                    <span class="text-blue-600 font-bold text-sm">1</span>
                  </div>
                  <div>
                    <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Right to Access</h4>
                    <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Request a copy of all your personal data</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="flex items-start">
                  <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-blue-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mr-3">
                    <span class="text-blue-600 font-bold text-sm">2</span>
                  </div>
                  <div>
                    <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Right to Rectification</h4>
                    <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Correct inaccurate or incomplete data</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="flex items-start">
                  <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-blue-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mr-3">
                    <span class="text-blue-600 font-bold text-sm">3</span>
                  </div>
                  <div>
                    <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Right to Erasure</h4>
                    <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Request deletion of your data ("right to be forgotten")</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="flex items-start">
                  <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-blue-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mr-3">
                    <span class="text-blue-600 font-bold text-sm">4</span>
                  </div>
                  <div>
                    <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Right to Restrict Processing</h4>
                    <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Limit how we use your data in certain circumstances</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="flex items-start">
                  <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-blue-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mr-3">
                    <span class="text-blue-600 font-bold text-sm">5</span>
                  </div>
                  <div>
                    <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Right to Data Portability</h4>
                    <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Receive your data in a portable format</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="flex items-start">
                  <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-blue-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mr-3">
                    <span class="text-blue-600 font-bold text-sm">6</span>
                  </div>
                  <div>
                    <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Right to Object</h4>
                    <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Object to certain types of data processing</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="flex items-start">
                  <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-blue-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mr-3">
